WEBVTT

02:13:02.668 --> 02:13:04.043
It feels like I’ve done both.

02:13:05.126 --> 02:13:06.418
How should I handle this.

02:13:08.876 --> 02:13:09.793
I need to kill him.

02:13:10.834 --> 02:13:13.543
If I don’t kill him, I’ll become
the one who killed my mother.

02:13:14.251 --> 02:13:16.251
I’ll remain as the one who murdered my own mother.

02:13:18.709 --> 02:13:19.709
I need to kill him.

02:13:22.376 --> 02:13:25.501
The one who is missing is not Shankar anymore,
he is Big Bull… Big Bull…

02:13:25.709 --> 02:13:27.043
Where is he?
Search him…

02:13:27.334 --> 02:13:28.459
Search the entire highway.
